results.description:
On vacation in Sweden I took my gear and sat down in a hazelbush.
I had seen some moose tracks the day before and I was really shure some animals would walk that way to the lake nearby. So I waited and waited and waited…
Long story short I woke up with a hurting back and dozens of gnat bites.
Demotivated I was about to grab my camera and walk back to the hut when I heard cracking noises.
Moments later this majestic bull moose walked by and sniffed at me and my backpack.
One of the best days in my life.
